<li id="cite_note-21"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-21">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><cite id="CITEREFMayPollitt1939" class="citation journal cs1">May, Geoffrey; Pollitt, Basil (1939). "English Legal Practice: Its Applicability to America". <i>Kentucky Law Journal</i>. <b>27</b> (2): 171.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=Kentucky+Law+Journal&amp;rft.atitle=English+Legal+Practice%3A+Its+Applicability+to+America&amp;rft.volume=27&amp;rft.issue=2&amp;rft.pages=171&amp;rft.date=1939&amp;rft.aulast=May&amp;rft.aufirst=Geoffrey&amp;rft.au=Pollitt%2C+Basil&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ABarrister" class="Z3988"></span></span>
</li>
<li id="cite_note-22"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-22">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text">This was confirmed by the Professional Conduct Committee of the Bar Council when it changed its rules on the usage of the description by individuals in 1970, Annual Statement of the Bar Council, 1969/70.</span>
</li>
<li id="cite_note-23"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-23">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><cite id="CITEREFR._Dinerstein1990" class="citation journal cs1">R. Dinerstein (1990). "Client-centred counselling: Reapppraisal and refinement". <i>Arizona Law Review</i>. <b>32</b>: 501, 541.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=Arizona+Law+Review&amp;rft.atitle=Client-centred+counselling%3A+Reapppraisal+and+refinement&amp;rft.volume=32&amp;rft.pages=501%2C+541&amp;rft.date=1990&amp;rft.au=R.+Dinerstein&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ABarrister" class="Z3988"></span></span>
</li>
<li id="cite_note-24"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-24">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><cite class="citation web cs1"><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://www.barstandardsboard.org.uk/regulatory-requirements/bsb-handbook/">"Bar Standard Board Handbook"</a>. Bar Standards Board.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft.btitle=Bar+Standard+Board+Handbook&amp;rft.pub=Bar+Standards+Board&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.barstandardsboard.org.uk%2Fregulatory-requirements%2Fbsb-handbook%2F&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ABarrister" class="Z3988"></span> Version 4.6 of the <i>BSB Handbook</i> came into force on 31 December 2020.</span>
</li>
<li id="cite_note-25"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-25">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><cite id="CITEREFRuairi.Kavanagh2014" class="citation web cs1">Ruairi.Kavanagh (2014-12-18). <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://gradireland.com/careers-advice/job-descriptions/barrister">"Barrister"</a>. <i>gradireland</i><span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved <span class="nowrap">2020-12-01</span></span>.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft.jtitle=gradireland&amp;rft.atitle=Barrister&amp;rft.date=2014-12-18&amp;rft.au=Ruairi.Kavanagh&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fgradireland.com%2Fcareers-advice%2Fjob-descriptions%2Fbarrister&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ABarrister" class="Z3988"></span></span>
</li>
<li id="cite_note-26"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-26">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><cite id="CITEREFBerger,_Marylin_J.1983" class="citation journal cs1">Berger, Marylin J. (Fall 1983). <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://scholarlycommons.law.northwestern.edu/cgi/viewcontent.cgi?referer=https://www.google.com/&amp;httpsredir=1&amp;article=1152&amp;context=njilb">"A Comparative Study of British Barristers and American Legal Practice and Education"</a>. <i>Northwestern Journal of International Business and Law</i>. <b>5</b> (3)<span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved <span class="nowrap">9 June</span> 2021</span>.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=Northwestern+Journal+of+International+Business+and+Law&amp;rft.atitle=A+Comparative+Study+of+British+Barristers+and+American+Legal+Practice+and+Education&amp;rft.ssn=fall&amp;rft.volume=5&amp;rft.issue=3&amp;rft.date=1983&amp;rft.au=Berger%2C+Marylin+J.&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fscholarlycommons.law.northwestern.edu%2Fcgi%2Fviewcontent.cgi%3Freferer%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2F%26httpsredir%3D1%26article%3D1152%26context%3Dnjilb&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ABarrister" class="Z3988"></span></span>
